type: software
title: "AgentFortress: Runtime Security Monitoring for AI Agents"
abstract: "AgentFortress provides real-time security monitoring, threat detection, and runtime protection for LLM-powered AI agents. It detects prompt injection, PII leakage, data exfiltration, jailbreaks, and anomalous behavior across LangChain, CrewAI, AutoGen, and OpenAI Agents SDK."
